STheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange"}}}